<span id="freeTextContainer7999624345462508066">I was reduced to tears. Never felt this way about a book of fiction for a really long time. A must read for everyone who loves good, well crafted &amp; sublime Indian fiction. Those who are into the spices themselves, this will be something beautiful to experience with all your senses. </span>

